76561197988110348,Recommended,428200,22515540,"Posted: 19 April, 2016",all,Just2McMuffin,"Only played for about 20min but I guess i understand the main things about this game.The game is really fun and well crafted. Its almost like the ""Project X Zone"" games for the 3DS. By that i mean that you controll a set amount of characters, you start with 3 and then as you progress you unlock more characters. You add or remove people from your group of 4 and follow a story based adventure where every stage is a combat scenario. Every character has 4 abilities, when you use one, the ability gets a cooldown and you switch to the next character and keep the combo chain going. The game is quite interesting, kinda funny story so far.The only thing that i need to comment on which could be improved is the UI and the text. Sometimes the screen dosn't fit with texts and icons cover some things around the screen. Regarding the text of the game, anyone could understand it except some parts like ""Titles"" for the stages being in chinese letters only. But there's alot of spelling errors such as. ""You unlocked a stage star (Icon) Use it to unlock next stag"" or ""then take care of the troublr on left"". Minor things but I'm looking forward to see how this game develops."
